texts.text: One day Akili, HappyHippo and LittleLion
were jumping outside.
They reached a beautiful river. Will Akili
and her friends be able to jump across the river?
Little‚ê¢Lion ran as fast as he could
towards the river.
He jumped up high and flew through the air.
Wow! LittleLion jumped as high as an antelope!
Happy‚ê¢Hippo ran fast as she could
towards the river.
She jumped up high and flew through the air.
Wow! HappyHippo jumped as high as a bird!
Akili ran as fast as she could towards the river.
But when she reached the river,
she was too afraid to jump.
LittleLion and HappyHippo encouraged Akili.

Akili started to believe in herself.
She decided to try again!
She jumped up and flew through the air.
Wow! Akili jumped as high as an airplane!
Wow! Akili did it!
HappyHippo and LittleLion were so proud of Akili!
The three friends jumped all afternoon.
They jumped over the flowers.
They jumped over the rocks!
